This is the Enhanced jQuery Placeholder plugin.

Features:

- Cross-browser & Cross-styling placeholder HTML5 attribute
- Support for password, textarea, text, email, search, url.



What's next?

- Code organize to easily customize settings
- May be check if the browser supports native css styling:

/* webkit */
::-webkit-input-placeholder { color:#999 }

/* mozilla */
:-moz-placeholder { color: #999 }